list.abstract: 《Disappointed》是由歌手Terry Dexter演唱的一首英文歌曲，于2012年6月发行，收录于专辑《欧美新歌速递》中。

yingyinNormal.en: Just tell her I can't come. She'll be disappointed if we don't show up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你就跟她说我有事去不了了嘛。如果我们不去，她会很失望的。

yingyinNormal.en: He will never be disappointed with you. You're the best thing that's ever happened to him. Thank you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他永远都不会对你失望的，你是他今生最好的礼物。谢谢。

yingyinNormal.en: In turn, son fails to protect the kingdom by giving me the key. Mum would be very disappointed. Wouldn't she?
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以，儿子为了保护这个国家就需要把钥匙给我，妈妈可是会很失望的，不是吗？

yingyinNormal.en: The Fourth of July means nothing anymore. Overcooked hot dogs and fireworks that always leave you disappointed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 国庆节已经变得毫无意义。烤焦的热狗，永远令你失望的焰火。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm very disappointed in your sister.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我对你姐失望透了。

yingyinNormal.en: Really, Amy? Gossip? I'm disappointed in you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你开玩笑吧？艾米？跟我聊八卦？我对你失望了。

yingyinNormal.en: I feel terrible. Please don't be too disappointed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我觉得很愧疚，求求你不要对我失望。

yingyinNormal.en: She's 93. She won't be disappointed for very long.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她都九十三岁了，也失望不了几年了。

yingyinNormal.en: And I could only make out one word. "Disappointed."
yingyinNormal.zh: 我勉强听到两个字，失望。

yingyinNormal.en: Well then, I'm sure your family will be very disappointed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那想必你家人会很失望。

yingyinNormal.en: For the record, I'm not disappointed. You know, you said I would be disappointed when I met you, but I'm not.
yingyinNormal.zh: 顺便说一下，我没有失望。你说过我见到你会失望，但是我没有。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm sorry I disappointed you. I am disappointed. But not because you didn't find it. But because you did. And you lied.
yingyinNormal.zh: 抱歉我让你失望了。我是失望。但不是因为你没找到。是因为你找到了。但你却撒谎了。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't want him to be disappointed with this life. With me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不想他对这种生活失望，和我一起的生活。

yingyinNormal.en: You're right. I'm not. Now are you satisfied? No. Just disappointed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你说的对，我不是，现在你满意了吗？不！我只是觉得失望。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm disappointed, Donald. But I understand. And I won't pressure you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我好失望，唐纳德。但我理解，我不会逼迫你。

yingyinNormal.en: Simba, I'm very disappointed in you. I know. You could've been killed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 辛巴，我对你非常失望，我知道你可能会死掉。

yingyinNormal.en: What did she say? Enough. I find I'm most disappointed in Tony Gillingham.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她说了什么？不少了，我对托尼·吉利安姆十分失望。

yingyinNormal.en: Dearest Papa, I hope you're not too disappointed. Don't be silly. Not at all.
yingyinNormal.zh: 亲爱的爸爸，我希望您没有太失望。别傻了，才不会呢。

yingyinNormal.en: I should have known. I expect big things from you. Well, you won't be disappointed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我早该想到，期待你有出色表现。你包准不会失望。

yingyinNormal.en: Look, try to see things from my point of view. I am extremely disappointed with my life.
yingyinNormal.zh: 听着，试着从我的角度考虑考虑，我对自己的生活失望透顶。
